<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Re:View - 내 오답 아카이브</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">Re:View</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/board">게시판</a>
                <a href="/write">오답작성</a>
                <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <header style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
            <h1>내 오답 아카이브</h1>
            <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">사용자: <strong><%= user.username %></strong>님, 지금까지 총 <strong><%= notes.length %>개</strong>의 오답을 기록하셨습니다.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="stats-grid" style="margin-bottom: 60px;">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="val"><%= notes.length %></span>
                <span class="lbl">기록한 오답</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box dark">
                <span class="val">Lv. <%= Math.floor(notes.length / 5) + 1 %></span>
                <span class="lbl">나의 기록 레벨</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 15px;">내가 작성한 글</h2>
            <div class="notes-list">
                <% if (notes && notes.length > 0) { %>
                    <% notes.forEach(note => { %>
                        <div class="card" style="position: relative;">
                            <a href="/post/<%= note.id %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;">
                                <span class="tag"><%= note.type_name || '기타' %></span>
                                <h3><%= note.title %></h3>
                                <p><%= note.solution.substring(0, 100) %>...</p>
                                <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999;">
                                    등록일: <%= new Date(note.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <div style="margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <a href="/post/<%= note.id %>/edit" class="btn" style="background: #ffa502; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 5px 10px;">수정</a>
                                <form action="/post/<%= note.id %>/delete" method="POST" onsubmit="return confirm('정말로 삭제하시겠습니까?');" style="display: inline;">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn" style="background: #ff4757; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 5px 10px;">삭제</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="card" style="text-align: center; padding: 40px; border-style: dashed;">
                        <p>아직 작성한 오답 노트가 없습니다.</p>
                        <a href="/write" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 20px;">첫 오답 기록하기</a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
